    <p>{`It would take us close to a thousand years of continuing the period of strongest increase in human power consumption to reach the sun’s total energy output.`}</p>
    <p>{`But I digress. My point is that solar energy is obviously by far the best long-term solution for all our energy needs and (perhaps slightly less obviously) - here comes the core message of this blog post - the best short term solution as well when combined with large-scale batteries.`}</p>
    <p>{`The price of solar has seen such a steady and rapid decrease that it won’t take much longer for it to drastically undercut every other method of energy generation humanity has yet developed.`}</p>
